data.description: Exquisite resort-like living - Four Seasons Mirage at Barnegat - at the Jersey Shore! Stunning natural lighting. The fine, stately character of your 3,400+ SF Sequoia Loft is evident in the fabulous layout. Bright - roomy - spacious. Vaulted cathedral ceilings are undeniably magnificent. Your dining room rolls oh so nicely into a chic living room. Two 1st-floor bedrooms, Two 2nd-floor bedrooms, 1st floor office/or 5th bedroom. Large chef's kitchen flows to a generously sized great room w/ gas fireplace. Fenced patio for relaxing evenings outdoors. Plus, you're invited to enjoy an abundance of amenities...the Clubhouse, indoor and outdoor pools, fitness room, card rooms, tennis courts, pitch and putt, bocce, pickle ball and more! Don't miss this chance to buyâ€”this home will not last long!
